article_title: Rep. Mark Takano goes the full Kanye on Sen. Ted Cruz's filibuster – twitchy.com
article_text:
We disagree with the sentiment, but it really would have been something if Rep. Mark Takano (D-Calif.) had crashed the Senate floor to do his Kanye West impression in person. A quick and dirty Photoshop will have to do, though.

. @RepMarkTakano Fail. — Jeff Scully (@JeffScully) September 24, 2013

Literally the dumbest thing I have ever seen RT @RepMarkTakano RT @RepMarkTakano: Ted Cruz, Ima let you finish but… pic.twitter.com/Q4rqYYWjuj — H (@HL_Tweets) September 24, 2013

Greatest filibuster of all time? What was that about again? Preserving late-term abortion and blocking stronger safety standards at abortion clinics.

.@RepMarkTakano Of course! There's nothing quite like a woman on her feet for hours arguing the merits of infanticide. @daveweigel — pjswan (@pjswan) September 24, 2013

Yes, but her pink sneakers were really cute!
